sentences: Beverly Caimen (born June 20, 1994), known mononymously as Beverly (ビバリー), is a Filipino pop singer based in Japan under the Avex Trax label.
Beverly Caimen was born on June 20, 1994 in Calamba, Laguna, Philippines as the third child to Ramon Vega Caimen and Leticia Valdez Lumbres, having a brother and two other sisters.

Beverly received a Best Performance nomination from Awit Awards and won the Harvest of Honors award from the National Commission for Culture and the Arts and the Best Performance award from the A Song of Praise Music Festival Year 3.
With Beverly finally in Japan in 2015, she attended singing and dancing workshops and signed with Avex Trax in 2016.
With Beverly finally in Japan in 2015, she attended singing and dancing workshops and signed with Avex Trax in 2016.
The reaction she received was very positive, which lead to her being included in the Disney Magical Pop Christmas album.
She also opened for Ariana Grande on her Dangerous Woman Tour on October 10, 2017 at Makuhari Messa.
Beverly released her debut album, Awesome, on May 31, 2017.
Beverly released her second album, 24, on June 20, 2018.
The album reached No. 16 on the Oricon Albums Chart and charted for a total of six weeks.
Beverly released her third album, Infinity, on December 4, 2019.
